title: Inside Out 2
plot: A sequel that features Riley entering puberty and experiencing brand new, more complex emotions as a result. As Riley tries to adapt to her teenage years, her old emotions try to adapt to the possibility of being replaced.

2666218 2667469 Embarrassment, get that out of there!

90767 94271 This is Joy, coming to you live

171181 172765 you know her, you love her...

305273 307692 they make the most wonderful thing of all.

316868 320997 all wrapped up in what some might call our masterpiece.
321164 323166 You know, one of the hardest challenges we found...

501011 503180 "We're not gonna think about that right now."
